snippet.title: 'Brutal Thoughts with Jack Black' #2: Human Video Game [HD]
snippet.description: The second episode of 'Brutal Thoughts with Jack Black'. Jack plugs himself into an elaborate contraption so he can act out the role of his character Eddie Riggs, which Tim Schafer kindly goes along with before revealing he has actual footage of Brütal Legend to share.
